## 📝 FICHIER 3: .env.example

Allez sur: https://github.com/yahiadevs-max/lims-app/new/main

**Nom du fichier:** `.env.example`

**Contenu:**

```env
# ============================================
# DATABASE CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
DB_HOST=mysql
DB_PORT=3306
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=root_password_change_me
DB_NAME=lims_db

# ============================================
# SERVER CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
PORT=3001
NODE_ENV=development
API_URL=http://localhost:3001

# ============================================
# FRONTEND CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api

# ============================================
# JWT & SECURITY
# ============================================
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_jwt_key_change_this_in_production_12345
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=your_refresh_secret_key_change_this_12345
JWT_EXPIRE=7d
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRE=30d

# ============================================
# AUTHENTICATION
# ============================================
TOTP_ISSUER=LIMS
TOTP_LABEL=Laboratory Management System

# ============================================
# EMAIL CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
EMAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
EMAIL_PORT=587
EMAIL_SECURE=false
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-password
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@lims.com

# ============================================
# LOGGING
# ============================================
LOG_LEVEL=debug
LOG_DIR=./logs

# ============================================
# REDIS (Optional - for caching/sessions)
# ============================================
REDIS_HOST=redis
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_PASSWORD=

# ============================================
# CORS
# ============================================
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:3001

# ============================================
# FILE UPLOAD
# ============================================
MAX_FILE_SIZE=10485760
UPLOAD_DIR=./uploads

# ============================================
# RATE LIMITING
# ============================================
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=900000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100

# ============================================
# PAGINATION
# ============================================
DEFAULT_PAGE_SIZE=10
MAX_PAGE_SIZE=100
